### Verificar servidor
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Criar um encontro
POST http://localhost:3001/encounters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emboscada na Floresta",
  "description": "Orcs atacam o grupo no caminho para Triel"
}

### Buscar encontro (substitui o ID depois de criar)
GET http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6



### Adicionar monstro ao encontro
POST http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/combatants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Orc Guerreiro",
  "initiative": 12,
  "hpMax": 15,
  "ac": 13,
  "isPlayer": false
}

### Adicionar jogador ao encontro
POST http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/combatants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dan",
  "initiative": 18,
  "hpMax": 28,
  "ac": 15,
  "isPlayer": true
}

### Iniciar o combate
POST http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/start

### Passar o turno
POST http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/next-turn

### Aplicar dano no Orc
PATCH http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/combatants/cmpvh20r10001k1spnivjld8o/hp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "valor": 8,
  "tipo": "dano"
}

### Curar o Dan
PATCH http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/combatants/cmpvh23tf0003k1spibxzt8nl/hp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "valor": 5,
  "tipo": "cura"
}

### Adicionar condição e exaustão no Dan
PATCH http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/combatants/cmpvh23tf0003k1spibxzt8nl/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "exhaustionLevel": 2,
  "conditions": ["poisoned", "prone"]
}

### Encerrar o combate
POST http://localhost:3001/encounters/cmpvgtdxb0000c2d4g9oe38u6/end